refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
stringldap_next_attribute resourcelink_identifier resourceresult_entry_identifier
Retrieves the attributes in an entry. The first call to ldap_next_attribute is made with the result_entry_identifier returned from ldap_first_attribute.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the next attribute in an entry on success and &false; on
 error.

